        reason: Doc path is normalized and restricted to same-origin /docs routes before iframe src is set.
        created: 2026-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
        expires: 2027-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
  javascript/HardcodedNonCryptoSecret:
    - backend/schema/scripts/apply-operation-descriptions.mjs:
        reason: OpenAPI description strings and operationId keys; not embedded credentials.
        created: 2026-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
        expires: 2027-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
    - frontend/src/modules/AuthStore.ts:
        reason: localStorage key name for session stack, not a secret value.
