        expires: 2027-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
  javascript/HTTPSourceWithUncheckedType:
    - backend/routes/users.js:
        reason: Setup-mode roles array is normalized to string[] before use.
        created: 2026-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
        expires: 2027-06-03T00:00:00.000Z
  javascript/PT:
    - .github/actions/infisical-oidc-load/infisical_oidc.py:
